title: Kate Flannery / Broken Ribs & Vocal Cords & Her Mother’s Emphysema
description: Sean and Dr. Wali talk about fingers in the butt, rust pee, and how Sean decides on which acting roles he takes. Kate Flannery talks about doing her own stunts on The Office, fracturing her rib, bruising her vocal cords, and her mother’s struggle with emphysema and lymphedema.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
